<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="M.C3.A9moire_politique_:_Muriel_Marland-Militello.2C_d.C3.A9put.C3.A9e"><a href="/wiki/Memoire_politique" title="Memoire politique" class="mw-redirect">Mémoire politique</a>&#160;: Muriel Marland-Militello, députée</span></h2>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:MurielMarlandMilitello.jpg" class="image" title="Muriel Marland-Militello"><img alt="Muriel Marland-Militello" src="/wiki/images/2/28/MurielMarlandMilitello.jpg" width="150" height="192" /></a></div>
